Many chemicals are used during processing for meat and fish. Some of these chemicals may produce some by products that may cause cancer.

fields.personal_info: Django is a powerful framework for writing Python web applications. Using a full-featured framework like Django allows you to get your applications and sites up and running quicker without having to worry about the common structural code to tie it together. Frameworks let you focus on the unique portions of your application and let the tools do the heavy lifting.
